ABOUT THE PROJECT (ANALYSING OLYMPIC GAME DATA):

In this project a data set of Olympic Games from 1896 to 2016 will be used. Attributes Information. This data set contains all the detail of athletes participated, country & city event took place, event year & season etc.

Column

Purpose of the project

    This set of data will be used to have useful insights and visualizations.
    The Data will be mined and analyzed to answer different questions, like:
    Which country won more medals?
    Which player won most medals?
    Comparing performance year wise.
    Visualizing top 10 countries.
    Which city hosted the event most times?
    Medal tally of all / few countries across the years.
    And so many.
